55.7	Bj%C3%B8rn_Lomborg	Bjørn Lomborg	Bjørn Lomborg (born January 6, 1965) is a Danish author, academic, and environmental writer. He is an adjunct professor at the Copenhagen Business School, director of the Copenhagen Consensus Centre and a former director of the Environmental Assessment Institute in Copenhagen. He became internationally known for his best-selling and controversial book The Skeptical Environmentalist.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bf/Bj%C3%B8rn_Lomborg_1.jpg/150px-Bj%C3%B8rn_Lomborg_1.jpg
